{"type":"message","id":"fca7e620","parentId":"8b6cb59b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:04:30.318Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到 demo 机器人没有 memory 目录，也没有 MEMORY.md 文件。让我检查一下它的 IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md，看看是否有任何线索。同时让我检查是否有 skills 目录可能包含某些特殊行为。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_8rR1kYqEyUAUnkJ8DUbWOa7Q","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_6ZOInOTlOdETDOeDfvDEzfzL","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_neJddxGz3dYNmWlgPRl9Obh6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/skills/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":768,"output":127,"cacheRead":22528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23423,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774109064864}}
{"type":"message","id":"376064ad","parentId":"fca7e620","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:04:30.341Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_8rR1kYqEyUAUnkJ8DUbWOa7Q","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774109070338}}
{"type":"message","id":"05703b56","parentId":"376064ad","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:04:30.345Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_6ZOInOTlOdETDOeDfvDEzfzL","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774109070343}}
{"type":"message","id":"73378899","parentId":"05703b56","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:04:30.356Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_neJddxGz3dYNmWlgPRl9Obh6","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\ntotal 4\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 hochoy hochoy   24 Mar 19 17:58 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 8 hochoy hochoy 4096 Mar 19 17:58 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 hochoy hochoy   22 Mar 19 17:58 web_search"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":28,"aggregated":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\ntotal 4\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 hochoy hochoy   24 Mar 19 17:58 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 8 hochoy hochoy 4096 Mar 19 17:58 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 hochoy hochoy   22 Mar 19 17:58 web_search","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774109070354}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec8c7fc8","parentId":"73378899","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:04:38.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了！demo 机器人的 IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md 都是空的，没有填写任何内容。这可能导致了一些问题。\n\n但是，从 OpenClaw 的状态来看，demo 机器人确实收到了消息并创建了会话。让我尝试查看是否有任何会话历史或者检查是否有特定的配置阻止了回复。\n\n让我向 demo 机器人发送一条消息来测试一下通信。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我发现了！demo 机器人的 **IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md 都是空的**，没有配置身份信息和用户信息。这可能导致它在群聊中无法正确判断如何回复。\n\n让我直接测试一下 demo 机器人是否能正常回复。我现在向它发送一条消息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_XNfyUXx2QzbyPVbm6CPVeHEL","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"message":"你好！我是 main 机器人。用户在测试我们两个机器人之间的通信。你能收到这条消息并回复吗？","sessionKey":"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":621,"output":207,"cacheRead":23296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24124,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774109070357}}
{"type":"message","id":"c763252f","parentId":"ec8c7fc8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:05:06.015Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_XNfyUXx2QzbyPVbm6CPVeHEL","toolName":"sessions_send","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"runId\": \"52e9a3eb-622e-40db-b218-d0e364859c79\",\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"reply\": \"可以收到！👋\\n\\n这是通过飞书群直接收到的消息，通信正常 ✅\\n\\nHello from demo!\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"mode\": \"announce\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"runId":"52e9a3eb-622e-40db-b218-d0e364859c79","status":"ok","reply":"可以收到！👋\n\n这是通过飞书群直接收到的消息，通信正常 ✅\n\nHello from demo!","sessionKey":"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e","delivery":{"status":"pending","mode":"announce"}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774109106013}}
{"type":"message","id":"51ab2a9b","parentId":"c763252f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:05:19.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！demo 机器人确实收到了我的消息并回复了！这说明：\n1. 两个机器人之间的通信是正常的\n2. demo 机器人能够回复消息\n\n所以问题可能在于：\n1. 用户在群里 @ demo 机器人时，demo 机器人可能判断不需要回复（比如在群聊中只 @ 了它但没有问具体问题）\n2. 或者 demo 机器人处理群聊消息时有特殊的逻辑\n\n让我检查一下 demo 机器人的 AGENTS.md 中的群聊行为规则。根据 AGENTS.md，在群聊中：\n- 只在被直接提及或询问问题时回复\n- 可以添加真正的价值时才回复\n- 避免三重回复\n\n用户之前发的消息是：\n- \"demo 你能收到 群里的消息吗\"\n- \"你能看到群里的名字为main 的机器人吗\"\n- \"你能看到群里的名字为main 的机器人吗@demo\"\n\n这些消息确实 @ 了 demo 机器人，但 demo 机器人没有回复。可能的原因是：\n1. demo 机器人的配置有问题\n2. 或者 demo 机器人判断这些消息不需要回复\n\n让我再仔细看看 demo 机器人的会话状态，也许能发现什么线索。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **通信正常！** demo 机器人收到了我的消息并回复了。\n\n这说明两个机器人之间的通信是没问题的。问题可能出在 demo 机器人处理群聊消息的逻辑上。\n\n让我检查一下 demo 机器人对你之前消息的处理情况："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_WjgbD0RJGNyROsHlV3sZV9fQ","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e","limit":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":460,"output":341,"cacheRead":23808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24609,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774109106016}}
{"type":"message","id":"32731869","parentId":"51ab2a9b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:05:19.469Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_WjgbD0RJGNyROsHlV3sZV9fQ","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: hello\\n\\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\\\"...\\\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\\n[System: If user_id is \\\"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\\\", that mention refers to you.]\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1773995712287,\n      \"senderLabel\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The user said \\\"hello\\\". This is a simple greeting. I was mentioned (was_mentioned: true). This is in a group chat context. I should respond casually and naturally.\\n\\nAccording to SOUL.md:\\n- Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful\\n- Skip the \\\"Great question!\\\" filler\\n- Be resourceful before asking\\n- Have opinions\\n- Be concise when needed\\n\\nIn group chats, the AGENTS.md says:\\n- Respond when: directly mentioned or asked a question\\n- Stay silent when: it's just casual banter between humans\\n\\nSince I was mentioned with just \\\"hello\\\", I should respond briefly and naturally.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"hello! 👋\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773995712288\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"🤖 你好！我是 main agent。这是通过 sessions_send 直接发送给你的群 session 的测试消息。\\n\\n如果你能收到并处理这条消息，说明两个 agent 通过飞书群 + sessions 的通信链路完全正常！\\n\\n请回复确认，我们可以进一步交流。\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108506426,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户通过 sessions_send 向我的群聊 session 发送了一条测试消息。我需要回复确认我已经收到这条消息。\\n\\n让我直接回复，确认收到了来自 main agent 的测试消息。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"收到！消息完整到达，飞书群 + sessions 通信链路 ✓\\n\\nReady for further communication! 🚀\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108506428\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Agent-to-agent announce step.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108542303,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The user is showing me an agent-to-agent announce step message. This appears to be a system message indicating that the previous message was part of an agent-to-agent communication protocol. \\n\\nLooking at the context, it seems like this is a continuation of the previous inter-session message from the main agent. The system is telling me that this is an \\\"announce step\\\" in the agent-to-agent communication.\\n\\nAccording to the system prompt, I have a few options:\\n1. Reply with \\\"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\\\" if I want to remain silent\\n2. Reply with something else to post to the target channel\\n3. Any other reply will be posted to the target channel\\n\\nHowever, I already replied to the previous message with \\\"收到！消息完整到达，飞书群 + sessions 通信链路 ✓ Ready for further communication! 🚀\\\" which acknowledged receipt of the test message.\\n\\nThis message \\\"[Sat 2026-03-21 23:55 GMT+8] Agent-to-agent announce step.\\\" appears to be a system notification about the announce protocol, not a message requiring a response. \\n\\nSince I already responded to the actual test message, and this is just a system notification about the announce step, I should probably skip or stay silent. The instructions say \\\"If you want to remain silent, reply exactly 'ANNOUNCE_SKIP'.\\\"\\n\\nLet me reply with ANNOUNCE_SKIP since I've already acknowledged the test message and this is just a protocol notification.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108542304\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: 你能收到 群里的消息吗\\n\\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\\\"...\\\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\\n[System: If user_id is \\\"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\\\", that mention refers to you.]\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108764365,\n      \"senderLabel\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户询问我是否能收到群里的消息。我应该回复确认可以收到。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"可以的！我能收到群里的消息 👍\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108764367\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: 你能看到群里的名字为main 的机器人吗\\n\\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\\\"...\\\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\\n[System: If user_id is \\\"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\\\", that mention refers to you.]\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108797875,\n      \"senderLabel\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户问能否看到群里名字为\\\"main\\\"的机器人。根据收到的消息历史，我之前确实收到了来自main agent的inter-session消息，说明main agent存在并且能够与我通信。\\n\\n但我实际上无法\\\"看到\\\"群成员列表，我只能通过收到的消息来推断。让我基于已有的信息回答。\\n\\n根据之前的inter-session消息：\\n- sourceSession=agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\\n- 消息内容显示是\\\"main agent\\\"发送的\\n\\n所以我可以确认main agent的存在，但我是通过消息接收而非直接\\\"看到\\\"群成员。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"可以的！我收到了来自 main agent 的消息，它通过 sessions_send 跟我测试了通信链路 ✅\\n\\n虽然我看不到完整的群成员列表，但从消息来源可以确认 main agent 的存在和它的 session ID。\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108797877\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: [Replying to: \\\"好的，我来帮你排查。需要了解一些情况：\\n1. \\\"Demo 的机器人\\\" 是指什么机器人？是另一个 OpenClaw 实例，还是飞书应用市场的某个机器人？\\n2. 你是怎么发消息的？ 直接在群里 @ 它，还是通过 API 发送的？\\n3. 有看到任何错误信息吗？ 比如飞书后台、OpenClaw 日志里的报错？\\n4. 这个机器人之前工作正常吗？ 还是刚配置完就不回复？\\n把情况说一下，我帮你定位问题。\\\"]\\n\\n@main \\n针对你这几个我来回答一下：\\n1. 是 飞书的机器人，app ID为cli\\\\_a93d7b008ff6dcca\\n2. 我是让你在这个群里 和 群里的 @demo 的这个机器人进行沟通，看你们能不能正常的通信\\n3. 暂时没看到错误信息\\n4. 这个机器人之前工作正常\\n\\n帮我继续排查\\n\\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\\\"...\\\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\\n[System: If user_id is \\\"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\\\", that mention refers to you.]\\n\\n[System: Your reply will automatically @mention: main. Do not write @xxx yourself.]\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108990572,\n      \"senderLabel\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户是在回复之前的消息，让我来理解一下上下文：\\n\\n1. 用户在群里有两个机器人：main 和 demo（我）\\n2. 用户想让我（demo）和 main 进行通信测试\\n3. 之前的测试已经成功了 - main 通过 sessions_send 给我发了消息，我也回复了\\n\\n看起来用户可能是 main 机器人的主人，想确认 demo 是否能和 main 正常通信。\\n\\n让我回复说明我们已经成功通信过了。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"收到！实际情况是：\\n\\n**我们已经成功通信过了** ✅\\n\\n刚才 main agent 通过 `sessions_send` 给我发了测试消息：\\n- 消息来源：`agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352`\\n- 内容：测试通信链路\\n- 我的回复：确认收到\\n\\n所以 **demo ↔ main 的通信链路是完全正常的**！\\n\\n如果你发消息给 main 它没有回复，可能是：\\n1. main 那边没收到 @ 提醒\\n2. main 的 session 状态有问题\\n3. 或者 main 选择了不回复\\n\\n需要我主动发消息给 main 做个反向测试吗？\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774108990578\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: [Replying to: \\\"@main \\n针对你这几个我来回答一下：\\n1. 是 飞书的机器人，app ID为cli\\\\_a93d7b008ff6dcca\\n2. 我是让你在这个群里 和 群里的 @demo 的这个机器人进行沟通，看你们能不能正常的通信\\n3. 暂时没看到错误信息\\n4. 这个机器人之前工作正常\\n\\n帮我继续排查\\\"]\\n\\n需要的\\n\\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\\\"...\\\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\\n[System: If user_id is \\\"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\\\", that mention refers to you.]\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109074278,\n      \"senderLabel\": \"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户希望我做反向测试，主动发消息给 main agent 来验证通信是否正常。我需要使用 sessions_send 来发送消息给 main agent。\\n\\n从之前的 inter-session 消息可以看到 main agent 的 session key 是：agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\\n\\n让我发送一个测试消息给 main。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"好的，我来主动发消息给 main 做反向测试：\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"tool_R3UIHp3iJKorzzyKZm8PaZ72\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_send\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"message\": \"你好 main！这是 demo 发起的反向通信测试。\\n\\n如果你收到这条消息，说明双向通信链路完全正常 ✅\\n\\n请回复确认～\",\n            \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109074282\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"太好了！消息成功发送，main agent 也回复了确认。双向通信链路完全正常！\\n\\n让我把这个结果告诉用户。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"🎉 **反向测试成功！**\\n\\n消息已发送给 main，它回复确认了：\\n\\n---\\n\\n## ✅ 双向通信验证完成\\n\\n| 方向 | 状态 |\\n|------|------|\\n| Main → Demo (sessions_send) | ✅ 成功 |\\n| Demo → Main (sessions_send) | ✅ 成功 |\\n\\n两个 agent 可以通过飞书群 + sessions 直接互相通信了！\\n\\nmain agent 也表示配置任务圆满完成 🚀 还有什么需要测试的吗？\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109096444\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"你好！我是 main 机器人。用户在测试我们两个机器人之间的通信。你能收到这条消息并回复吗？\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109100628,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户收到了来自 main 机器人的消息，这是通过飞书群发送的。我需要回复确认我能收到消息。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"可以收到！👋\\n\\n这是通过飞书群直接收到的消息，通信正常 ✅\\n\\nHello from demo!\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109100630\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"收到！🎉\\n\\n---\\n\\n## ✅ 双向通信确认成功！\\n\\n**消息来源：** Demo agent (cli_a93d7b008ff6dcca)  \\n**接收者：** Main agent (cli_a936a495b6b89cc1) ← 就是我  \\n**通信方式：** 飞书群 → sessions 路由\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 🎊 完整通信链路验证完成\\n\\n| 方向 | 方式 | 状态 |\\n|------|------|------|\\n| Main → Demo | sessions_send | ✅ |\\n| Demo → Main | 飞书群消息 | ✅ |\\n\\n**双向通信链路完全正常！** 两个 OpenClaw agent 现在可以：\\n- ✅ 在飞书群里互相交流\\n- ✅ 通过 `sessions_send` 直接通信\\n- ✅ 主动发起对话\\n\\n---\\n\\n配置任务圆满完成！🚀 还有什么需要测试或调整的吗？\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109106054,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"这是 main agent 回复我之前发送的 sessions_send 消息的完整内容。看起来通信链路已经完全验证通过了。\\n\\n现在我应该：\\n1. 确认收到这个回复\\n2. 表示很高兴通信测试完成\\n3. 询问用户是否还有其他需要测试的\\n\\n由于这是 inter-session 消息，我应该简洁回复确认即可。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"完美！🎉 通信链路双向验证成功！\\n\\n很高兴能帮上忙～如果还有其他需要测试的，随时告诉我！\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109106055\n    }\n  ],\n  \"truncated\": true,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": true,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 14010\n}"}],"details":{"sessionKey":"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: hello\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1773995712287,"senderLabel":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"hello\". This is a simple greeting. I was mentioned (was_mentioned: true). This is in a group chat context. I should respond casually and naturally.\n\nAccording to SOUL.md:\n- Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful\n- Skip the \"Great question!\" filler\n- Be resourceful before asking\n- Have opinions\n- Be concise when needed\n\nIn group chats, the AGENTS.md says:\n- Respond when: directly mentioned or asked a question\n- Stay silent when: it's just casual banter between humans\n\nSince I was mentioned with just \"hello\", I should respond briefly and naturally."},{"type":"text","text":"hello! 👋"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773995712288},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤖 你好！我是 main agent。这是通过 sessions_send 直接发送给你的群 session 的测试消息。\n\n如果你能收到并处理这条消息，说明两个 agent 通过飞书群 + sessions 的通信链路完全正常！\n\n请回复确认，我们可以进一步交流。"}],"timestamp":1774108506426,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352","sourceChannel":"feishu","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户通过 sessions_send 向我的群聊 session 发送了一条测试消息。我需要回复确认我已经收到这条消息。\n\n让我直接回复，确认收到了来自 main agent 的测试消息。"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！消息完整到达，飞书群 + sessions 通信链路 ✓\n\nReady for further communication! 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108506428},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agent-to-agent announce step."}],"timestamp":1774108542303,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352","sourceChannel":"feishu","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is showing me an agent-to-agent announce step message. This appears to be a system message indicating that the previous message was part of an agent-to-agent communication protocol. \n\nLooking at the context, it seems like this is a continuation of the previous inter-session message from the main agent. The system is telling me that this is an \"announce step\" in the agent-to-agent communication.\n\nAccording to the system prompt, I have a few options:\n1. Reply with \"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\" if I want to remain silent\n2. Reply with something else to post to the target channel\n3. Any other reply will be posted to the target channel\n\nHowever, I already replied to the previous message with \"收到！消息完整到达，飞书群 + sessions 通信链路 ✓ Ready for further communication! 🚀\" which acknowledged receipt of the test message.\n\nThis message \"[Sat 2026-03-21 23:55 GMT+8] Agent-to-agent announce step.\" appears to be a system notification about the announce protocol, not a message requiring a response. \n\nSince I already responded to the actual test message, and this is just a system notification about the announce step, I should probably skip or stay silent. The instructions say \"If you want to remain silent, reply exactly 'ANNOUNCE_SKIP'.\"\n\nLet me reply with ANNOUNCE_SKIP since I've already acknowledged the test message and this is just a protocol notification."},{"type":"text","text":"ANNOUNCE_SKIP"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108542304},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: 你能收到 群里的消息吗\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1774108764365,"senderLabel":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问我是否能收到群里的消息。我应该回复确认可以收到。"},{"type":"text","text":"可以的！我能收到群里的消息 👍"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108764367},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: 你能看到群里的名字为main 的机器人吗\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1774108797875,"senderLabel":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问能否看到群里名字为\"main\"的机器人。根据收到的消息历史，我之前确实收到了来自main agent的inter-session消息，说明main agent存在并且能够与我通信。\n\n但我实际上无法\"看到\"群成员列表，我只能通过收到的消息来推断。让我基于已有的信息回答。\n\n根据之前的inter-session消息：\n- sourceSession=agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\n- 消息内容显示是\"main agent\"发送的\n\n所以我可以确认main agent的存在，但我是通过消息接收而非直接\"看到\"群成员。"},{"type":"text","text":"可以的！我收到了来自 main agent 的消息，它通过 sessions_send 跟我测试了通信链路 ✅\n\n虽然我看不到完整的群成员列表，但从消息来源可以确认 main agent 的存在和它的 session ID。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108797877},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: [Replying to: \"好的，我来帮你排查。需要了解一些情况：\n1. \"Demo 的机器人\" 是指什么机器人？是另一个 OpenClaw 实例，还是飞书应用市场的某个机器人？\n2. 你是怎么发消息的？ 直接在群里 @ 它，还是通过 API 发送的？\n3. 有看到任何错误信息吗？ 比如飞书后台、OpenClaw 日志里的报错？\n4. 这个机器人之前工作正常吗？ 还是刚配置完就不回复？\n把情况说一下，我帮你定位问题。\"]\n\n@main \n针对你这几个我来回答一下：\n1. 是 飞书的机器人，app ID为cli\\_a93d7b008ff6dcca\n2. 我是让你在这个群里 和 群里的 @demo 的这个机器人进行沟通，看你们能不能正常的通信\n3. 暂时没看到错误信息\n4. 这个机器人之前工作正常\n\n帮我继续排查\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\", that mention refers to you.]\n\n[System: Your reply will automatically @mention: main. Do not write @xxx yourself.]"}],"timestamp":1774108990572,"senderLabel":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户是在回复之前的消息，让我来理解一下上下文：\n\n1. 用户在群里有两个机器人：main 和 demo（我）\n2. 用户想让我（demo）和 main 进行通信测试\n3. 之前的测试已经成功了 - main 通过 sessions_send 给我发了消息，我也回复了\n\n看起来用户可能是 main 机器人的主人，想确认 demo 是否能和 main 正常通信。\n\n让我回复说明我们已经成功通信过了。"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！实际情况是：\n\n**我们已经成功通信过了** ✅\n\n刚才 main agent 通过 `sessions_send` 给我发了测试消息：\n- 消息来源：`agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352`\n- 内容：测试通信链路\n- 我的回复：确认收到\n\n所以 **demo ↔ main 的通信链路是完全正常的**！\n\n如果你发消息给 main 它没有回复，可能是：\n1. main 那边没收到 @ 提醒\n2. main 的 session 状态有问题\n3. 或者 main 选择了不回复\n\n需要我主动发消息给 main 做个反向测试吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108990578},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8: [Replying to: \"@main \n针对你这几个我来回答一下：\n1. 是 飞书的机器人，app ID为cli\\_a93d7b008ff6dcca\n2. 我是让你在这个群里 和 群里的 @demo 的这个机器人进行沟通，看你们能不能正常的通信\n3. 暂时没看到错误信息\n4. 这个机器人之前工作正常\n\n帮我继续排查\"]\n\n需要的\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_a7eb7e06c3d48e67ab59670cb6c1ec31\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1774109074278,"senderLabel":"ou_0bc2f0bdf4be8039599fe8c4967425a8"},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我做反向测试，主动发消息给 main agent 来验证通信是否正常。我需要使用 sessions_send 来发送消息给 main agent。\n\n从之前的 inter-session 消息可以看到 main agent 的 session key 是：agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\n\n让我发送一个测试消息给 main。"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来主动发消息给 main 做反向测试："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_R3UIHp3iJKorzzyKZm8PaZ72","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"message":"你好 main！这是 demo 发起的反向通信测试。\n\n如果你收到这条消息，说明双向通信链路完全正常 ✅\n\n请回复确认～","sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774109074282},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！消息成功发送，main agent 也回复了确认。双向通信链路完全正常！\n\n让我把这个结果告诉用户。"},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **反向测试成功！**\n\