,\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"[Sat 2026-03-21 23:55 GMT+8] 🤖 你好！我是 main agent。这是通过 sessions_send 直接发送给你的群 session 的测试消息。\\n\\n如果你能收到并处理这条消息，说明两个 agent 通过飞书群 + sessions 的通信链路完全正常！\\n\\n请回复确认，我们可以进一步交流。\"}],\"timestamp\":1774108506426,\"provenance\":{\"kind\":\"inter_session\",\"sourceSessionKey\":\"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\"sourceChannel\":\"feishu\",\"sourceTool\":\"sessions_send\"}}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"da729f56\",\"parentId\":\"898d5902\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-21T15:55:10.113Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户通过 sessions_send 向我的群聊 session 发送了一条测试消息。我需要回复确认我已经收到这条消息。\\n\\n让我直接回复，确认收到了来自 main agent 的测试消息。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"收到！消息完整到达，飞书群 + sessions 通信链路 ✓\\n\\nReady for further communication! 🚀\"}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"kimi-coding\",\"model\":\"k2p5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":7034,\"output\":65,\"cacheRead\":8448,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":15547,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1774108506428}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"279f8aeb\",\"parentId\":\"da729f56\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-21T15:55:42.305Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"[Sat 2026-03-21 23:55 GMT+8] Agent-to-agent announce step.\"}],\"timestamp\":1774108542303,\"provenance\":{\"kind\":\"inter_session\",\"sourceSessionKey\":\"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\"sourceChannel\":\"feishu\",\"sourceTool\":\"sessions_send\"}}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"a80a56aa\",\"parentId\":\"279f8aeb\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-21T15:55:51.635Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user is showing me an agent-to-agent announce step message. This appears to be a system message indicating 