{"type":"message","id":"63ba0b41","parentId":"b98a760d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:12:17.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到只有 `feishu-demo-allowFrom.json` 和 `feishu-pairing.json` 等文件存在，但没有 `feishu-demo.json` 主凭证文件。\n\n但奇怪的是，main 账号也没有 `feishu-main.json` 文件，只有 `feishu-main-allowFrom.json`。\n\n让我重新分析一下。日志显示的错误是读取 `feishu-demo.json` 失败，但我没有看到类似的错误发生在 main 上。\n\n让我检查一下 main 的日志，看看是否有不同的行为。实际上，我应该检查一下 delivery-queue 是否有任何线索。\n\n问题可能是：1. demo 的飞书应用在初始化时没有正确获取 token\n2. demo 的飞书应用权限配置有问题\n3. demo 的飞书应用没有被添加到群聊让我直接问用户一个关键问题：demo 的飞书应用是否被添加到了这个群聊中？","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下更详细的日志，看看消息发送时的具体情况："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_7ji0qInt05vOfFevscUIqAav","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw logs --limit 200 --plain 2>&1 | grep -A5 -B5 \"demo\" | tail -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":893,"output":244,"cacheRead":103680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104817,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774109527816}}
