eishu_chat tool\n2026-03-21T16:11:02.110Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n2026-03-21T16:11:02.113Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n2026-03-21T16:11:02.117Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\n2026-03-21T16:11:11.805Z error [tools] read failed: ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/hochoy/.openclaw/config.json'\n2026-03-21T16:11:28.082Z error [tools] read failed: ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/hochoy/.openclaw/credentials/feishu-demo.json'\n2026-03-21T16:11:57.290Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\n2026-03-21T16:11:57.302Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n2026-03-21T16:11:57.305Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n2026-03-21T16:11:57.309Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n2026-03-21T16:11:57.314Z info plugins {\"subsystem\":\"plugins\"} feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774109543772}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7ccb2fb","parentId":"3ff582f5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:12:34.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题已经明确了。日志显示：`error [tools] read failed: ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/hochoy/.openclaw/credentials/feishu-demo.json'`这表明系统在尝试读取 demo 的飞书凭证文件时失败了。\n\n现在让我总结一下发现的问题并给出解决方案。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔍 问题定位完成\n\n找到根本原因了！\n\n### 问题\n日志显示：\n```\nerror [tools] read failed: ENOENT: no such file or directory, \naccess '/home/hochoy/.openclaw/credentials/feishu-demo.json'\n```\n\n**demo 机器人的飞书凭证文件缺失**，导致它虽然能**接收**消息，但无法**发送**回复到飞书群。\n\n### 为什么我能收到 demo 的回复？\n因为我（main 机器人）和 demo 是通过 `sessions_send` 直接通信的，这个不依赖飞书 API。但 demo 发送回复到飞书群需要调用飞书 API，而凭证缺失导致发送失败。\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 解决方案\n\n需要重新初始化 demo 的飞书凭证。请运行以下命令："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_qfvbfkbtQSOCIpGROHaSbZET","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw setup feishu demo --interactive 2>&1 || echo \"Setup command not available, trying alternative...\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":885,"output":277,"cacheRead":104448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105610,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774109543776}}
