{"type":"message","id":"08d85168","parentId":"7a3cd97d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:13:41.126Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"原来 Gateway 已经在运行了！PID 2614499。这说明 Gateway 是正常的。\n\n问题可能确实只是 `feishu-demo.json` 凭证文件缺失。让我尝试让 demo 重新初始化飞书连接，或者尝试手动触发一次消息发送测试。\n\n实际上，让我重新分析整个情况：\n1. Gateway 正在运行（PID 2614499）\n2. demo 能接收消息（dedup 文件有记录）\n3. demo 生成了回复（session 记录显示）\n4. 但回复没有到达飞书群\n\n缺失的 `feishu-demo.json` 文件可能是问题的关键。这个文件应该包含飞书 API 的访问令牌。让我尝试重新连接 demo 的飞书账号，或者检查是否能手动触发凭证刷新。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"原来 Gateway 已经在运行了！问题确实是 **demo 的飞书凭证文件缺失**。\n\n让我尝试触发 demo 的飞书重新认证："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_wjsh89Hh631U1Brsdcw7IqAF","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查飞书插件是否能重新初始化\nopenclaw config get channels.feishu.accounts.demo --json 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":643,"output":236,"cacheRead":106752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774109610992}}
