{"type":"message","id":"4e5e4245","parentId":"0f3b27ed","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:43:46.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我收到了 demo 的回复：\"测试回复：我能正常收到和发送消息！\"。这表示 sessions_send 通信是正常的。\n\n但用户能否在群里看到这个回复，取决于 demo 是否能成功调用飞书 API 发送消息。\n\n让我检查一下日志，看看消息发送是否成功。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我已通过 `sessions_send` 收到 demo 的回复：**\"测试回复：我能正常收到和发送消息！\"**\n\n现在请检查一下群里是否出现了这条消息？如果还是看不到，说明问题确实是 **demo 无法调用飞书 API 发送消息**。\n\n让我查看日志确认发送状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_hIUQ6Cj1n3dPJDFHWvoaP20i","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw logs --limit 50 --plain 2>&1 | grep -i \"send\\|reply\\|deliver\" | tail -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":350,"output":168,"cacheRead":110336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110854,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774111421062}}
